title: Eklecticafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic international cuisine and desserts at this eclectic cafe with a funky decor. An old cabin adorned with lights, flower pots, vintage decorations and old wooden floors. Staff has a list of all vegan options when asked. Tofu can be exchanged for eggs in all the breakfast dishes.
